title: Dax Riggs Blood or Love Rough Mix [Full]
description:
This is the rough mix of the album.. It was recorded at Dax&#039;s home in Houma, LA.
It&#039;s labled [Full] because it has one other track from the sessions that was never released with them. The song is the original version of "Ghost movement", but was called "Flowers". Its rumored there is one more song that is part of these sessions.
Ive also added a picture of a limited edition shirt.
